{{version031}}
{{flavour|Drains the life force of any nearby creatures, healing the user depending on the damage dealt.}}

'''Drain Life''' is a monsters-only spell that deals [[negative energy]] damage to every enemy in the caster's [[line of sight]] and restores half the damage dealt to the caster. In effect, this allows the enemy to [[smite]] you and all your allies and heal itself in a single action. [[Negative energy resistance]] reduces its effect, negating it entirely at rN+++.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
{{CBA|0.32|Drain Life's damage will be increased. Also, it will ignore AC again.}}
*Prior to [[0.29]], Drain Life didn't check AC.
*Drain Life was added in [[0.12]].

[[Category:Monster spells]]
